\section{$\mathrm{Li}_{\mathrm{x}} \mathrm{SiO}_{\mathrm{y}}$ Thin Films}
 USAb Chemistry and Nanoscience Center, National Renewable Energy Laboratory, Golden, $\mathrm{CO}, 80401$, USA

' Department of Chemistry, Colorado School of Mines, Golden, CO, 80401, USA

d Lawrence Berkeley National Laboratory, Berkeley, CA 94720, USA

